 "timestamp": "2026-04-15T13:25:16Z",
 "wikitext": "{{CSS|content=<nowiki>\n@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Inconsolata');\n/* Font */\nhtml .resizable-container, .page-content h1, .page-content h2, .page-content h3, .page-content h4, .page-content h5, .page-content h6 {\n    font-family: 'Inconsolata'</nowiki>}}{{DISPLAYTITLE:<span style=\"color:red\">{</span><span style=\"color:red\">{DISPLAYTITLE:</span>Level Level (Joke)<span style=\"color:red\">}</span><span style=\"color:red\">}</span>}}\n<div style=\"border:6px solid #009811;margin:1.0em;padding: 10px 20px\">This is a joke page. It is not meant to be taken seriously and is only for laughs. <span style=\"color:#0099ff\"><nowiki>'''</nowiki></span>'''This page is released on April Fools but it is meant to be a permanent page. Do not add a delete template.'''<span style=\"color:#0099ff\"><nowiki>'''</nowiki></span></div>\n<div style=\"border:6px solid #009811;margin:1.0em;padding: 10px 20px\"><center><big><span style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><center><big></nowiki></span><span style=\"color:#0099ff\"><nowiki>'''</nowiki></span>'''ANOMALY ALERT'''<span style=\"color:#0099ff\"><nowiki>'''</nowiki></span><span style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki></big></center></nowiki></span></big><br><span style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><br></nowiki></span></center>This is an emergency. A parasitic level has been slowly infecting the pages of newcomers, even if they are completely unrelated to it. It is only a matter of time when they start appearing on actual high-quality pages, so those contracted pages are deleted by moderators at an instant to prevent further spreading. The M.E.G. is working hard to study this level that references itself on random pages.</div><div class=\"mw-collapsible\" id=\"mw-customcollapsible-view\"><div class=\"mw-customtoggle-view\"><center><span style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><div class=\"mw-customtoggle-view\"><center></nowiki></span>>VIEW<span style=\"color:#009811\"><nowiki></center></div></nowiki></span></center></div></div><div class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\" id=\"mw-customcollapsible-view\"><span style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><div class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\" id=\"mw-customcollapsible-view\"></nowiki></span>\n<div style=\"border:6px solid #009811;margin:1.0em;padding: 10px 20px\"><center><big><span style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><center><big></nowiki></span><span style=\"color:#0099ff\"><nowiki>'''</nowiki></span>'''CLASS 0, INFOHAZARD'''<span style=\"color:#0099ff\"><nowiki>'''</nowiki></span><span style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki></big></center></nowiki></span></big></center></div>\n<div style=\"color:red\"><span>_</span>_NOTOC__</div>\n== <span style=\"color:#0099ff\">==</span> Description <span style=\"color:#0099ff\">==</span> ==\n<span style=\"color:#0099ff\"><nowiki>'''</nowiki></span>'''Level Level'''<span style=\"color:#0099ff\"><nowiki>'''</nowiki></span>, also known as \"Template:Levels\", is an anomalous level that manifests its presence in various new pages, which is something that has never been seen before in [[The Backrooms|<span style=\"color:#ff6600\">[<nowiki>[</nowiki><u>the Backrooms</u><nowiki>]</nowiki>]</span>]].<div style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><br></nowiki></div>\n[[File:Levelception.png|thumb|250px|Level Level.]]<span style=\"color:#ff6600\">[<nowiki>[</nowiki><u>File:Levelception.png</u>|</span>thumb|250px|Level Level.<span style=\"color:#ff6600\">]<nowiki>]</nowiki><br></span>Level Level takes place in a level, which looks like an average level , like [[Level 0|<span style=\"color:#ff6600\">[<nowiki>[</nowiki>Level 0]<nowiki>]</nowiki></span>]]. The level transcludes itself inside another level, which then transclude itself inside another level, creating an infinite loop of levels.<div style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><br></nowiki></div><div style=\"color:#319998\"><nowiki><!--I know this sounds really confusing, but just bear with me here.--></nowiki></div>\nThe level, similar to some levels, does not have entities that inhabit most levels, this is probably due to the level's unstable nature in the level, that forbids the survival of the entities.<div style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><br></nowiki></div><div style=\"color:#319998\"><nowiki><!--Um... reader, just continue reading, ignore the weird text, okay?--></nowiki></div>\nPages that mention this level will slowly have its description being replaced with the word \"level\". It occurs after the page about the level is created. The quality this level have in the level that makes the level level level level-<div style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><br></nowiki></div><div style=\"color:#319998\"><nowiki><!--STOP!!! Phew, that was close reader, this isn't the first time it has happened. Sorry for the inconvenience reader, I'll put the table up for ya.--></nowiki></div>\n<div style=\"color:#0000fe\">{| class=\"article-table\"</div>\n{| class=\"article-table\"\n|-\n!\n!Effects\n|-\n|0-10 minutes\n|Nothing happens to the page, as the phenomenon has not taken into effect yet.\n|-\n|10-30 minutes\n|The word \"level\" may seldomly appear in the page where it does not make any sense.\n|-\n|30 minutes to 1 hour\n|The word \"level\" appears much more often, being inserted in a bunch of different places. Sentences now stop making sense.\n|-\n|Above 1 hour\n|Every word is replaced with \"level\".\n|}\n<div style=\"color:#0000fe\">|}</div>\n<div style=\"color:#319998\"><nowiki><!--Sorry for what happened, reader, as you can see, this page will get more corrupted as time goes on. I, as the narrator, has the ability to delay the inevitable. You can now continue to the next section.--></nowiki></div>\n== <span style=\"color:#0099ff\">==</span> Entrances & Exits <span style=\"color:#0099ff\">==</span> ==\n<span style=\"color:#0099ff\">*</span> There are no confirmed entrances.<br>\n<span style=\"color:#0099ff\">*</span> There are no confirmed exits to [[Level 1|<span style=\"color:#ff6600\">[<nowiki>[</nowiki>Level 1]<nowiki>]</nowiki></span>]].\n<div style=\"color:#319998\"><nowiki><!--Wait what? Is... is the page still broken? What does this even mean?--></nowiki></div>\n== <span style=\"color:#0099ff\">==</span> Infectious Property <span style=\"color:#0099ff\">==</span> ==\nCompared to the actual level itself, it is perhaps most known for invading itself into newcomers' pages. They appear in the form of <span style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>}}</span>, commonly seen at the bottom of their pages, like a dirty stain on a piece of cloth.<div style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><br></nowiki></div>\nThis is very <span style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>}}</span>, as this template can <span style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>}}</span> into other pages, which <span style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>}}</span> the <span style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>}}</span> to <span style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>}}</span> <span style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>}}</span> <span style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>}}</span>...<div style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><br></nowiki></div>\n<div style=\"color:#319998\"><nowiki><!--Oh no, not again! This dreaded template!--></nowiki></div><div class=\"mw-collapsible\" id=\"mw-customcollapsible-ohno\"><div class=\"mw-customtoggle-ohno\"><div style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Collapse</u>|<span style=\"color:#cc01ff\">initial=</span><span style=\"color:#7622ff\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>}}</span>|<span style=\"color:#cc01ff\">final=</span><span style=\"color:#7622ff\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>}}</span>|<span style=\"color:#cc01ff\">num=</span><span style=\"color:#7622ff\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>|<span style=\"color:#cc01ff\">curse=</span><span style=\"color:#5544ff\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>}}</span>}}</span>|<span style=\"color:#cc01ff\">body=</span>?????}}</div></div></div><div class=