lor:black;background:white\">&<span>ems</span>p;</mark><mark style=\"color:black;background:white\">&<span>ems</span>p;</mark><mark style=\"color:black;background:white\">&<span>ems</span>p;</mark><mark style=\"color:black;background:white\">&<span>ems</span>p;</mark><mark style=\"color:black;background:white\">&<span>ems</span>p;</mark><mark style=\"color:black;background:white\">&<span>ems</span>p;</mark><span style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki></center></nowiki></span></center><br>\n<div style=\"color:#319998\"><nowiki><!--Random code spams! I don't know what any of them means!--></nowiki></div><br><br>\n<center><div style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><center></nowiki></div><div style=\"color:#de0034\"><nowiki></blockquote></math></ref></q></caption></bdi></bdo></colgroup></nowiki><div style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Levels</u>}}</div><br><nowiki></blockquote></math></ref></q></caption></bdi></bdo></colgroup></nowiki><br><br><br><nowiki></blockquote></math></ref></q></caption></bdi></bdo></colgroup></nowiki></div><div style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki></center></nowiki></div></center><br><div style=\"color:#319998\"><nowiki><!--We've reached the nowiki bunker! Click on it will allow you to enter it.--></nowiki><br><nowiki><!--But reader, I forgot to tell you one thing.--></nowiki><br><nowiki><!--You see, I can't enter the bunker, or else I'll die.--></nowiki><br><nowiki><!--I suppose this is where we depart.--></nowiki><br><nowiki><!--I'll be your final barrier.--></nowiki><br><br><center><nowiki><!---------------------------------------------------------------------></nowiki></center><br></div><div class=\"mw-collapsible\" id=\"mw-customcollapsible-nowiki\"><div style=\"color:#009801\" class=\"mw-customtoggle-nowiki\"><nowiki><nowiki></nowiki><span></nowi</span>ki></div></div>\n<div class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\" id=\"mw-customcollapsible-nowiki\"><div style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><nowiki></nowiki></div>You have entered the bunker.<br>You are now safe, but...<br>How are you gonna read the rest of the page now?<br>...<br>Guess you'll never know what the level is. It's the most eye-catching part of a page.<br>It must be infuriating to see this template over and over again.<br>So please stop adding them to your pages.<br>Period.<div style=\"color:#009801\"><span></nowi</span>ki></div></div><br><br>{{User:Brightened_Star/Credits|infi=<span style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>{{</nowiki><u>Collapse</u><nowiki>|</nowiki><span style=\"color:#cc01ff\">initial=</span><span style=\"color:#fe019a\"><nowiki>{{{1|</nowiki></span></span>Open Credits<span style=\"color:#fe019a\"><nowiki>}}}</nowiki><nowiki>|</nowiki></span><span style=\"color:#cc01ff\">final=</span><span style=\"color:#fe019a\"><nowiki>{{{2|</nowiki></span>Close Credits<span style=\"color:#fe019a\"><nowiki>}}}</nowiki></span><span style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>|</nowiki></span><span style=\"color:#cc01ff\">num=</span><span style=\"color:#fe019a\"><nowiki>{{{3|</nowiki></span>Made by [[User:Brightened_Star|<span style=\"color:#ff6600\"><nowiki>[[</nowiki><u>User:Brightened_Star</u>|</span><span class=\"onlylight\"><span style=\"color:#3a3a3a\">Star</span></span><span class=\"onlydark\"><span style=\"color:#e6e6e6\">Star</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff6600\"><nowiki>]]</nowiki></span>]].<span style=\"color:#fe019a\"><nowiki>}}}</nowiki></span><span style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>|</nowiki></span><span style=\"color:#cc01ff\">body=</span><span style=\"color:#009801\"><nowiki><tabber></tabber></nowiki></span><span style=\"color:#9900fe\"><nowiki>}}</nowiki></span>}}<br><div style=\"color:#ff6600\"><nowiki>[[</nowiki><u>Category:Joke</u>]] <nowiki>[[</nowiki><u>Category:Joke Levels</u>]] <nowiki>[[</nowiki><u>Category:Infohazard</u>]] <nowiki>[[</nowiki><u>Category:Levels</u>]][[Category:Joke]][[Category:Joke Levels]][[Category:Infohazard]][[Category:Levels]]\n</div><!--redff0000 orangeff6600 blue0099ff green009801 pinkfe019a teal319998 purple9900fe 2purpl